query:
SELECT date, 
       total_spend_meta, 
       total_spend_google,
       total_leads,
       vip_sales
FROM daily_kpis 
WHERE date >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 7 DAY)
ORDER BY date DESC
LIMIT 10
